07:06.942 --> 07:08.777
Mum,

07:09.211 --> 07:12.412
I have some news that I think
will make you really happy.

07:12.413 --> 07:14.948
Your paper on gender and
the anti-nuclear movement

07:14.949 --> 07:15.950
