you that research position?

07:19.521 --> 07:22.022
- Oh my god, Kaitlyn.
- Even better.

07:22.023 --> 07:23.825
I'm in love.

07:24.259 --> 07:26.025
You?

07:26.026 --> 07:27.896
Yeah, I know.

07:28.497 --> 07:29.864
But he's wonderful.

07:29.865 --> 07:30.864
He?

07:30.865 --> 07:31.866
<i>What?</i>

07:31.867 --> 07:33.234
