any guy who comes along.

07:45.846 --> 07:47.914
I know, honey. It's just that-

07:47.915 --> 07:50.417
it's just that if you had been a lesbian,

07:50.418 --> 07:52.253
I would've been fine with that.

07:52.254 --> 07:54.155
Lesbians get fewer STDs,

07:54.156 --> 07:56.525
no unwanted pregnancies.

07:56.791 --> 07:59.059
Not that I don't think you
would make a wonderful mother

07:59.060 --> 08:00.994
in the distant future.

08:00.995 --> 08:02.796
But, hey.

08:02.898 --> 08:04.999
So, you're in love!

08:05.000 --> 08:07.669
With a man, yay!

08:07.802 --> 08:09.003
What's he like?

08:09.004 --> 08:10.905
Well, he's a writer.

08:10.906 --> 08:11.905
Oh, shit.

08:11.906 --> 08:13.073
Oh, no. No, no, no, no.

08:13.074 --> 08:14.575
He's nothing like-

08:14.576 --> 08:17.578
and I-I know you won't
have time to meet him this-

08:18.012 --> 08:19.412
this week, but I'm-

08:19.413 --> 08:21.047
I'm sure you'd love him.

08:21.048 --> 08:22.316
I have time.

08:22.317 --> 08:23.917
<i>Really?</i>

08:23.951 --> 08:26.587
Shouldn't you be flying to Machu Picchu?

08:26.588 --> 08:27.587
Machu Picchu?

08:27.588 --> 08:29.189
<i>Yeah, remember when we-</i>

08:29.190 --> 08:30.058
we made you go to Disneyland?

08:30.059 --> 08:32.225
You kept saying that you'd always dreamt

08:32.226 --> 08:33.293
of going to Machu Picchu

08:33.294 --> 08:34.327
and here you were

08:34.328 --> 08:36.130
in fucking Disneyland.

08:36.163 --> 08:37.163
Well, that was years ago,

08:37.164 --> 08:38.898
and I'm not going anywhere.

08:38.899 --> 08:40.701
<i>Well,</i>

08:40.902 --> 08:41.902
you know what I mean.

08:41.903 --> 08:43.169
I would love to meet him.

08:43.171 --> 08:45.505
I just want you to see what an amazing job

08:45.506 --> 08:46.374
you did as a mother.

08:46.375 --> 08:49.109
Zoe's got that fantastic new career,

08:49.110 --> 08:51.545
and I found my soul-mate.

09:01.056 --> 09:03.725
What shall I read?

09:05.125 --> 09:06.627
Middlemarch.

09:09.865 --> 09:12.333
A good 899 pages.

09:12.600 --> 09:14.769
It's too long.

09:20.475 --> 09:23.009
<i>I know what I don't</i>

09:23.010 --> 09:24.912
want to read.

09:28.115 --> 09:30.785
<i>What's the shortest?</i>

09:39.427 --> 09:41.328
Hi, I was ah...

09:42.129 --> 09:44.364
You know, I'd quite like to ah...

09:44.365 --> 09:47.035
<i>I mean, if you would, um.</i>

09:48.168 --> 09:52.840
I know we haven't, uh,
been doing it much lately,

09:53.240 --> 09:56.509
<i>uh, which is probably
my fault, but um.</i>

09:56.510 --> 09:58.912
You know, my back's a lot better,

09:58.913 --> 10:00.714
and um,

10:01.015 --> 10:03.017
<i>I just don't want you to die</i>

10:03.018 --> 10:04.918
<i>wishing you'd had more sex,</i>

10:04.919 --> 10:07.120
which is apparently quite common.

10:07.121 --> 10:09.123
<i>At the same time, I don't
want you to think that</i>

10:09.124 --> 10:11.124
I'm the kind of man who would

10:11.125 --> 10:13.761
force a dying woman to-

10:17.065 --> 10:19.032
And it's not because, uh,

10:19.033 --> 10:21.435
I'm facing the fact that
I might have to spend

10:21.436 --> 10:23.303
the rest of my life without sex.

10:23.304 --> 10:24.404
No, no, no, no.

10:24.405 --> 10:26.340
<i>That's-that's, no.</i>

10:26.341 --> 10:28.008
No, this is-

10:28.009 --> 10:29.310
this is really just

10:29.311 --> 10:31.112
not about me.

10:31.278 --> 10:32.880
<i>No, so-</i>

10:36.150 --> 10:38.952
I'm just letting you know that, uh,

10:39.086 --> 10:41.088
any-time you want,

10:42.090 --> 10:44.125
I am available,

10:45.225 --> 10:46.694
<i>not now, I would
guess, from your face.</i>

10:46.695 --> 10:48.162
<i>You know, that's fine,
you read your book.</i>

10:48.163 --> 10:49.562
That's fine, that's fine.

10:49.563 --> 10:51.365
But, uh,

10:51.566 --> 10:53.066
any-time in the next

10:53.067 --> 10:55.236
24, 48 hours,

10:56.236 --> 10:58.238
I'm here for you.

10:59.975 --> 11:02.110
Also 72 hours.

11:02.210 --> 11:04.110
How many nights home do you have left?

11:04.111 --> 11:05.713
- Four.
- Four!

11:05.714 --> 11:08.383
<i>Four, that's loads of time, four.</i>

11:09.183 --> 11:11.185
<i>Yeah, or-or-or
cuddles.</i>

11:11.186 --> 11:13.186
Cuddles, too, all the cuddles you want.

11:13.187 --> 11:14.754
And if the cuddles lead to sex,

11:14.755 --> 11:16.757
yay!

12:08.243 --> 12:10.044
You

12:10.278 --> 12:13.081
