13:36.597 --> 13:37.730
We have been married forever.

13:37.731 --> 13:39.133
Not forever.

13:39.134 --> 13:40.533
Yeah, and I'm not that predictable.

13:40.534 --> 13:43.237
I could, theoretically, still surprise you.

13:45.606 --> 13:46.606
No.

13:46.607 --> 13:47.608
No, you couldn't.

13:47.609 --> 13:49.410
Please, go to bed.

13:49.844 --> 13:50.610
- <i>Are you sure?</i>
- Yes, I'll see you later.

13:50.611 --> 13:52.412
Bye, sweetheart.

13:53.413 --> 13:56.217
Okay, well, I'm just upstairs.

13:57.284 --> 13:58.284
So,

13:58.285 --> 13:59.519
