14:03.658 --> 14:05.392
If the only husband I had ever had

14:05.393 --> 14:06.759
was a lying little shit

14:06.760 --> 14:08.662
who cheated on me when
I had a newborn baby!

14:08.663 --> 14:10.631
Why are you exaggerating?

14:10.831 --> 14:12.532
She wasn't newborn, she was

14:12.533 --> 14:13.633
six months old.

14:13.634 --> 14:15.234
This is insane.

14:15.235 --> 14:16.769
You know, I might
surprise you all and live.

14:16.770 --> 14:18.437
That would be fantastic.

14:18.438 --> 14:20.239
<i>Well, wouldn't you only
want me because I'm dying?</i>

14:20.240 --> 14:21.642
