14:21.643 --> 14:22.643
for the rest of your life,

14:22.644 --> 14:24.644
you never would have got
on that plane in London.

14:24.645 --> 14:26.279
No.

14:26.280 --> 14:27.281
I've changed.

14:27.282 --> 14:28.282
Well, I haven't.

14:28.283 --> 14:30.450
I still hate you and I
want you out of my house

14:30.451 --> 14:32.652
by the time I get up in the
morning, do you understand?

14:32.653 --> 14:35.055
Unless you want to be the first to die.

14:40.928 --> 14:43.598
I can read Middlemarch.

14:47.335 --> 14:48.801
<i>I'm smart.</i>

14:48.802 --> 14:50.537
I read fast.

14:50.538 --> 14:52.339
