31:03.442 --> 31:05.710
Because she is the love of my life.

31:05.711 --> 31:07.513
That's why.

31:09.449 --> 31:10.916
"She was
humiliated to find herself

31:10.917 --> 31:13.586
<i>a mere victim of feeling,</i>

31:14.387 --> 31:18.190
