33:07.800 --> 33:10.435
You can't blame me for trying.

33:10.436 --> 33:11.770
I mean, it's not over 'till it's over.

33:11.771 --> 33:13.405
Yeah, it's not a football match,

33:13.406 --> 33:15.074
