for making her go to

35:33.045 --> 35:34.046
Disneyland instead.

35:34.047 --> 35:35.046
You were eight.

35:35.047 --> 35:36.047
<i>It's not your fault.</i>

35:36.048 --> 35:37.817
Tom should have known better.

35:37.818 --> 35:39.084
I would have taken her to Machu Picchu.

35:39.085 --> 35:40.084
Ah, come on.

35:40.085 --> 35:41.720
Everybody loves Disneyland.

35:41.721 --> 35:43.122
Peanut?

35:43.123 --> 35:46.058
<i>You remember me videoing
