36:12.751 --> 36:14.754
You asked for this?

36:14.987 --> 36:16.120
Oh, thank you, yeah.

36:16.121 --> 36:18.290
Just leave it there.

36:19.826 --> 36:21.893
<i>Are you sure you're okay, Grace?</i>

36:21.894 --> 36:24.296
Yeah, I'm fine.

36:24.697 --> 36:26.700
Machu Picchu.

36:26.833 --> 36:28.667
I went there.

36:29.268 --> 36:31.271
Did you?

36:31.371 --> 36:33.506
