36:41.581 --> 36:43.781
<i>We could use some inspiration.</i>

36:43.782 --> 36:45.584
Or

36:45.885 --> 36:48.921
Depressing reminder of
what failures we've become.

36:48.922 --> 36:50.924
But they're beautiful.

36:54.594 --> 36:55.627
Hey, hey, careful.

36:55.628 --> 36:57.796
