37:35.835 --> 37:37.069
I'm-

37:37.070 --> 37:38.303
Oh, sorry.

37:38.304 --> 37:40.171
I'm sorry I-

37:40.172 --> 37:41.172
I apologize.

37:41.173 --> 37:43.343
