41:42.447 --> 41:43.881
So now you want him back.

41:43.882 --> 41:45.082
Well, over my dead body.

41:45.083 --> 41:46.584
If it's dead bodies we're talking about,

41:46.585 --> 41:48.419
I think I might just
have the advantage here.

41:48.420 --> 41:49.587
Excuse me.

41:49.588 --> 41:50.522
