48:14.407 --> 48:15.573
<i>I tell you what.</i>

48:15.574 --> 48:17.875
It's been so nice having Zoe for company

48:17.876 --> 48:19.678
while she tried out that new job.

48:19.679 --> 48:21.479
You've been a fantastic stepmother,

48:21.480 --> 48:23.448
and I really appreciate that.

48:23.449 --> 48:24.982
