48:42.501 --> 48:44.368
<i>I never wanted a baby of my own.</i>

48:44.369 --> 48:46.638
Who wants to clean up somebody's shit?

48:46.639 --> 48:48.707
<i>Now I wonder, you know,</i>

48:48.708 --> 48:51.442
